==English==
===Expression===
'''[[no]] [[problem]]'''

#certainly (''said when granting a request'')
#:''Porter, can you help me with my bags?'' &mdash; ''No problem, sir.''
#no thanks is necessary (''said in response to an expression of gratitude'')
#:''Thank you. &mdash; No problem.''

====Synonyms====
*(''certainly''): [[certainly]], [[of course]], [[yes]]
*(''no thanks is necessary''): [[don't mention it]], [[it's nothing]], [[it was nothing]], [[not at all]], [[no prob]], [[no probs]], [[no worries]], [[you're welcome]]

